Date-Indiction version 0.01
===========================

Compute a year's indiction as used in old Russian
chronicles. Christian and Byzantine (with epoch on March 1, 5508 BCE)
aerae are supported.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Exporter

